      <guid>http://localhost:1313/gear/renogy-100w-slim-solar-panels-stealth-promaster-setup/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Slim panels are popular in stealth-oriented builds because they keep roof profile lower and layout more flexible.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;my-4 rounded-md border p-3 text-sm opacity-90&#34;&gt;Disclosure: Some links may be affiliate links. If you buy, we may earn a commission at no extra cost to you.&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;span class=&#34;inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md px-4 py-2 font-semibold shadow-sm border border-transparent bg-neutral-900 text-white hover:bg-neutral-700 opacity-60 cursor-not-allowed&#34; aria-disabled=&#34;true&#34;&gt;Link coming soon&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h2 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Pros&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;pros&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;span&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#pros&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Modular layout makes phased expansion easy.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Slim format helps stealth and roof clearance constraints.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Strong documentation and accessory ecosystem.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h2 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Cons&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;cons&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;span&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#cons&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Higher price per watt versus some budget alternatives.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Performance depends heavily on mounting and airflow.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h2 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Who It’s For&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;who-its-for&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;span&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#who-its-for&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Builders who care about stealth roof profile.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;First-time DIY users who need documented install paths.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h2 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Still Worth It?&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;still-worth-it&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;span&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#still-worth-it&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Yes, especially for modular growth and parts availability.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
